    <h1>Semantic Search</h1>
    <p class="description">Search technology that interprets the meaning, context, and intent behind a query — not just the literal words. The shift from keyword matching to semantic understanding changed how Google ranks content and how SEOs should write it.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
